  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My name is Joshua Degani.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My date of birth is October 26, 1924, and I was born in Leipzig.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, before I got the name or took the name Degani, my name was Habergrutz, so was the name of my parents.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I changed the name in Israel together with my brother and called our-- myself-- we called ourselves Degani, which is a Hebrew word with a source of [?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Degan. ?] So as from then on, we are known as Degani.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I prepared some small resume.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To tell it all would take a lot of time, but at least I will try to give certain short description of what it was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My parents were quite wealthy because when my father married, he entered into a business arrangement in textiles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had employees and a car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A car was something very significant at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was a merchant, or a trader, in textiles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I then later on became-- wanted to become more aware of the activities when I grew up, so I tried to get some documentations.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I visited Leipzig a few years ago, I could find in the telephone book of [? then ?] and what do you call-- or what we call here yellow pages-- [INAUDIBLE] the registration of my father, Chaim Habergrutz, as textile merchant at the place where we lived, which was [?",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Humboldtstrasse ?] 27.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was very happy about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the telephone, we were also listed at the time that shows that we lived there, and we-- my father came there from Poland, and-- not directly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was before active in-- in trade in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
